Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫同学你这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道漆黑烈焰使堕入暗黑世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  过去的习惯一不小心又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者跟邪王真眼是由恋人契约相连的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又算啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快撒盐  樟叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：日本传统观念中「盐」有净化、祛灵的作用，\N在客人走后说「撒盐」则意指再也不想见到这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来哥哥你们不是不睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了  这也是魔法魔王少女的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有  本来就是我们睡着了的不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银杏高中远东魔术午睡结社之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对阵红叶丘高中Siesta同好会的练习比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不觉得能赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在都不知道她们是不是醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们毫无疑问是梦中世界的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前说好了输了你们就解散
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望滥用午睡部这名字的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少一个是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想都赢不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡得饱饱的  皮肤光溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还能做的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在道歉的话说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个社团也不是那么随便的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次遇见六花的时候我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我们真正的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探查不可视境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是活动不仅限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们的结社
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟六花你们一起就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方可是个中二病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大家总不被理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却认真努力着  这些跟午睡部很像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远东魔术午睡结社之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地Vanishment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂吧  现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩断吧  神经
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(620,656)}Vanishment  this  world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧  这个世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个睡梦世界是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Avalon  Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瓦隆粉碎击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Mjolnir  Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆战锤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去资格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(680,656)}Dark·Flame  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被漆黑烈焰吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去资格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去资格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(740,656)}Circadian  Rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NREM杀法  昼夜节律崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：NREM，非快速动眼睡眠  (Non-Rapid  Eye  Movements)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Destiny  Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运之环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有着如此强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真起来的话  都可以君临天下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要守护那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Sleeper's  Wake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡者的觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香学姐  茴香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君  你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了哦  我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香  感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  睡同学她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了  说是自己完败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们不用解散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然  明天还要跟冒牌大人一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着的时候  做了个很有趣的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放此力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Lightning  Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷电爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这个  雷属性的技能也完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩  凸守也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级的  你又在我衣服上动手脚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊  冒牌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是和什么都搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少东张西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是什么都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全也不午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能在这里睡觉是我现在最幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守  雷电
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听别人说话
